{"tid":2435743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"年過半百丨韓美魔女牙醫自爆曾與著名歌手拍拖3年","createTime":"2021-03-06T13:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T13:22:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1de3ba7285633bb05d800b78b53041079d310f20","tid":2435743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/77IQoU3Wre7RWnW1gDQhNfYIpVk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S2C3SGYTPFDHXA4RAFBAC5PYNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F77IQoU3Wre7RWnW1gDQhNfYIpVk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS2C3SGYTPFDHXA4RAFBAC5PYNA.jpg&h=bdf1a783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國年過50歲（1969年出生）的美女牙醫兼YouTuber李秀珍，因為樣貌及身材都完全不似年過半百而引來各界關注，加上她又孖住年約19歲的女兒一起經營YouTube頻道做網紅，而且曾自認靚過40歲女神金泰希，成功惹來網民的熱議。<br />\n<br />\n愛在頻道爆料<br />\n而李秀珍不時都愛在頻道中爆料，她之前就自爆被年輕27歲的男友求婚，遭女兒反對。而近日李秀珍又在頻道自爆曾和一名歌謠界歌手拍了3年拖，再次引起熱議。李秀珍近日在頻道上傳題為《在夜店被男朋友抓走的故事（著名藝人）》的片段，並透露：「20多年前和朋友一起去菲律賓旅行時，導遊姐姐和我們一起去夜店，那時我們已29歲了，男生們說自己是17歲，我們苦惱了很久才說是20歲，而他們就把我們送到酒店大廳。有個男孩子問我拿電話，旁邊的朋友就說我在韓國有一名很有名的歌手男友。而去完旅行回來後，和曾是歌手的男朋友分手了，我亦和別人結婚了。我之所以有這麼多的故事，是因為我年紀大，活得很久。」<br />\n<br />\n網民大感好奇<br />\n由於李秀珍自爆曾與著名歌手談戀愛，所以令不少網民好奇不已，並紛紛留言問是邊個。李秀珍則說：「他一度很火熱，在《歌謠Top 10》中獲得了第一名，是深受女生喜愛的歌手。當時，大家都會認識那位歌手。」她又自爆每當自己在夜店喝醉後，歌手男友就會突然出現帶她離開，對於大家不斷追問，李秀珍就避忌說：「他現在可能會和某個人結婚，生活得很好。」不過她直認因為對方，自己曾一度有想當歌手的念頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1r2j5Fc2DtFv120y4GivcqlhDgs=/802x2251/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I6WXQ3BQWVDKLEZU3F47ZETJPQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1r2j5Fc2DtFv120y4GivcqlhDgs%3D%2F802x2251%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI6WXQ3BQWVDKLEZU3F47ZETJPQ.png&h=7d1e1729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1HveUKw435sL_rdfU_IhnX12VLw=/802x1078/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HOFDCPE4JNFYTDSGPL7FM7JYGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1HveUKw435sL_rdfU_IhnX12VLw%3D%2F802x1078%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHOFDCPE4JNFYTDSGPL7FM7JYGE.jpg&h=30adb3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210306/N4LA225WDRB5PJT73QQYM4FLUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210306%2FN4LA225WDRB5PJT73QQYM4FLUI%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=2417024d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210306%2FN4LA225WDRB5PJT73QQYM4FLUI%2F&h=4f07c5c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210306/N4LA225WDRB5PJT73QQYM4FLUI/</a>"},{"pid":"fe1261518afb6981afb1a5547c0e96d54bd2cb68","tid":2435743,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"哇....<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f44af5b7108e48a149cff49bd5c82f5f830c08","tid":2435743,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"韓紋身師自爆與著名歌手拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d991bae0f462b597a1abae28b052629a742e24e6","tid":2435743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5f44af5b7108e48a149cff49bd5c82f5f830c08","tid":2435743,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"韓紋身師自爆與著名歌手拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:10:37.000Z","msg":"邊位二打六<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi